Dialogue Text: A wandering soul? Maybe one who's still searching for a purpose perhaps?
Hahaha don't mind me! Taking readings for other people has always been my hobby.
Do you remember the readings you took?
As part of my job as a scholar, spiritual things always caught my attention.
Hm... I no longer have the materials I need but simple readings should be no problem!
Yeah! I've heard that there's a certain ruins around here. I'm sure that would make a good spot!
Do you still do fortune readings now?
Does the place we're going to have anything to do with that?
I have taken a lot in the past but there's one that stood out to me the most.
It was such a rare reading that I couldn't just ignore it!
I wonder if mine would be rare too...
People often carry burdens of their own but this customer in particular had a lifelong burden to carry... I hope he's taking it easier now wherever he is...
Haha we'll never know until we see it for ourselves!
